---
// Roots.astro - Filosofía y enfoque técnico
---

<section
  id="sobre-mi"
  class="pt-32 pb-20 px-6 w-full container mx-auto"
  aria-labelledby="roots-heading"
>
  <!-- Header -->
  <header class="mb-20 flex flex-col items-start gap-4">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2 animate-fade-in-up">
      <span class="w-12 h-[1px] bg-emerald-500/30"></span>
      <span
        class="font-label text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-emerald-400/80"
        >Filosofía de Trabajo</span
      >
    </div>
    <h2
      id="roots-heading"
      class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-headline leading-[0.9] text-emerald-50 animate-slide-in-left"
    >
      Raíces del <br />
      <span class="italic text-emerald-300">Desarrollo.</span>
    </h2>
  </header>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-8 md:gap-10">
    <!-- Card 1: Core Approach (Large) -->
    <div
      class="md:col-span-8 bg-emerald-950/20 blob-card p-10 md:p-16 border border-emerald-500/10 relative overflow-hidden group hover:border-emerald-500/20 transition-all"
    >
      <div
        class="absolute -top-24 -right-24 w-64 h-64 bg-emerald-500/5 rounded-full blur-[100px] group-hover:bg-emerald-500/10 transition-all"
      >
      </div>
      <div class="relative z-10 space-y-8">
        <div
          class="w-16 h-16 bg-emerald-500/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-400"
        >
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m12 2 10 5v10l-10 5-10-5V7Z"></path><path d="m7 7 5 3 5-3"></path><path d="M12 10v12"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <h3 class="text-4xl font-headline text-emerald-50">
            Sistemas que Perduran.
          </h3>
          <p class="text-emerald-100/90 text-lg font-body max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
            Soy Maitén Oviedo. Empecé programando robots con Arduino y
            participando en ferias de ciencias en Mendoza, donde aprendí que si
            los cimientos no son sólidos, nada funciona. No creo en el software
            descartable; construyo sistemas que se pueden leer, mantener y
            escalar, sin complicaciones innecesarias. Cuando no estoy codeando,
            seguro me encontrás tomando mate o haciendo algún trekking por la
            montaña.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-6 pt-4">
          <div class="h-[1px] w-24 bg-emerald-500/30"></div>
          <span class="font-label text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-emerald-300/80 italic flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-emerald-500"></span> Estándares de Ingeniería
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Card 2: Vitales del Frontend -->
    <div
      class="md:col-span-4 bg-emerald-950/30 blob-card p-10 border border-emerald-500/10 flex flex-col justify-between gap-12 group"
    >
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
          <div
            class="w-10 h-10 bg-emerald-500/5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-400 border border-emerald-500/10"
          >
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 12h-4l-3 9L9 3l-3 9H2"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <span class="font-label text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-emerald-300/90">Vitales del Frontend</span>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-end border-b border-emerald-500/10 pb-3">
            <span class="text-emerald-100/80 font-label text-[9px] uppercase tracking-widest">Performance</span>
            <span class="text-emerald-50 font-headline text-2xl">100</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-end border-b border-emerald-500/10 pb-3">
            <span class="text-emerald-100/80 font-label text-[9px] uppercase tracking-widest">Accesibilidad</span>
            <span class="text-emerald-50 font-headline text-2xl">100</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-end border-b border-emerald-500/10 pb-3">
            <span class="text-emerald-100/80 font-label text-[9px] uppercase tracking-widest">SEO</span>
            <span class="text-emerald-50 font-headline text-2xl">100</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 bg-emerald-500/5 rounded-2xl border border-emerald-500/5 film-grain">
        <p class="text-[11px] font-body italic text-emerald-300/80 leading-relaxed">
          "Priorizo la mantenibilidad a largo plazo sobre el hackeo rápido de corto alcance."
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Card 3: IA como Ecosistema -->
    <div
      class="md:col-span-12 bg-emerald-950/20 blob-card p-10 md:p-16 border border-emerald-500/10 relative overflow-hidden group hover:border-emerald-500/20 transition-all duration-700"
    >
      <div class="absolute -bottom-32 -right-32 w-96 h-96 bg-emerald-500/5 rounded-full blur-[120px] group-hover:bg-emerald-500/10 transition-all"></div>
      <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-64 h-64 bg-emerald-400/3 rounded-full blur-[100px]"></div>

      <div class="relative z-10 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-10 items-start">
        <div class="lg:col-span-4 space-y-6">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-emerald-500/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-400 border border-emerald-500/15 shrink-0">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="4"></circle><line x1="4.93" y1="4.93" x2="9.17" y2="9.17"></line><line x1="14.83" y1="14.83" x2="19.07" y2="19.07"></line><line x1="14.83" y1="9.17" x2="19.07" y2="4.93"></line><line x1="4.93" y1="19.07" x2="9.17" y2="14.83"></line></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-headline text-emerald-50">IA como Ecosistema.</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-emerald-100/90 text-base font-body leading-relaxed">
            No uso la IA para autocompletar código. Trabajo con un ecosistema orquestado: un agente principal que razona y delega, y sub-agentes especializados que ejecutan con acceso a MCPs, skills y contexto de proyecto.
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 pt-2">
            <div class="h-[1px] w-16 bg-emerald-500/30"></div>
            <span class="font-label text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-emerald-300/70 italic">Gentle-AI Ecosystem</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="lg:col-span-8 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
          <div class="p-6 bg-emerald-900/20 rounded-2xl border border-emerald-500/10 space-y-3">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-emerald-500/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-400">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"></polygon></svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="font-label text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-emerald-300">Orquestador</h4>
            <p class="text-emerald-100/70 text-xs font-body leading-relaxed">Un agente central razona sobre el objetivo, optimiza contexto y tokens, y coordina sin ejecutar directamente.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="p-6 bg-emerald-900/20 rounded-2xl border border-emerald-500/10 space-y-3">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-emerald-500/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-400">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"></line><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"></line></svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="font-label text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-emerald-300">Sub-agentes</h4>
            <p class="text-emerald-100/70 text-xs font-body leading-relaxed">Agentes especializados con acceso a MCPs, skills y archivos de contexto como CLAUDE.md. Cada uno trabaja en su dominio.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="p-6 bg-emerald-900/20 rounded-2xl border border-emerald-500/10 space-y-3">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-emerald-500/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-400">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"></polyline></svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="font-label text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-emerald-300">Contexto Optimizado</h4>
            <p class="text-emerald-100/70 text-xs font-body leading-relaxed">El orquestador preserva contexto entre sesiones y minimiza tokens sin perder información crítica del proyecto.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="p-6 bg-emerald-900/20 rounded-2xl border border-emerald-500/10 space-y-3">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-emerald-500/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-400">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"></path><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"></polyline><line x1="16" y1="13" x2="8" y2="13"></line><line x1="16" y1="17" x2="8" y2="17"></line><polyline points="10 9 9 9 8 9"></polyline></svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="font-label text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-emerald-300">SDD</h4>
            <p class="text-emerald-100/70 text-xs font-body leading-relaxed">Spec Driven Development: propuesta, specs y diseño antes de una línea de código. Cada cambio tiene contrato explícito.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="p-6 bg-emerald-900/20 rounded-2xl border border-emerald-500/10 space-y-3">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-emerald-500/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-400">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="9 11 12 14 22 4"></polyline><path d="M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="font-label text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-emerald-300">TDD</h4>
            <p class="text-emerald-100/70 text-xs font-body leading-relaxed">El test define el comportamiento esperado antes de la implementación. Red → Green → Refactor, sin atajos.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="p-6 bg-emerald-900/20 rounded-2xl border border-emerald-500/10 space-y-3">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-emerald-500/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-400">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><ellipse cx="12" cy="12" rx="10" ry="4"></ellipse><path d="M2 12c0 4.418 4.477 8 10 8s10-3.582 10-8"></path><path d="M2 12V6c0-4.418 4.477-8 10-8s10 3.582 10 8v6"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="font-label text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-emerald-300">Engram</h4>
            <p class="text-emerald-100/70 text-xs font-body leading-relaxed">Memoria persistente entre sesiones. Decisiones, bugs y convenciones sobreviven compactaciones y arranques en frío.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Card 4: Código Adaptable -->
    <div
      class="md:col-span-12 lg:col-span-6 bg-emerald-950/20 blob-card p-12 border border-emerald-500/10 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-10 items-center hover:bg-emerald-900/10 transition-colors"
    >
      <div class="w-full md:w-40 h-40 bg-emerald-900/20 organic-mask overflow-hidden border border-emerald-500/10 film-grain shrink-0">
        <div class="w-full h-full flex items-center justify-center bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-500/5 to-transparent">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-emerald-500/30"><polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"></polyline><polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"></polyline></svg>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-headline text-emerald-50">Código Adaptable</h3>
        <p class="text-emerald-100/90 text-base font-body leading-relaxed">
          Diseño sistemas modulares que pueden evolucionar sin fricción. La adaptabilidad no es un extra, es una necesidad en cualquier arquitectura moderna.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Card 5: Cimientos Sólidos -->
    <div
      class="md:col-span-12 lg:col-span-6 bg-emerald-950/20 blob-card p-12 border border-emerald-500/10 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-10 items-center hover:bg-emerald-900/10 transition-colors"
    >
      <div class="w-full md:w-40 h-40 bg-emerald-900/20 organic-mask overflow-hidden border border-emerald-500/10 film-grain shrink-0">
        <div class="w-full h-full flex items-center justify-center bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-500/5 to-transparent">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-emerald-500/30"><path d="M12 2v4"></path><path d="M12 18v4"></path><path d="M4.93 4.93l2.83 2.83"></path><path d="M16.24 16.24l2.83 2.83"></path><path d="M2 12h4"></path><path d="M18 12h4"></path><path d="M4.93 19.07l2.83-2.83"></path><path d="M16.24 7.76l2.83-2.83"></path></svg>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-headline text-emerald-50">Cimientos Sólidos</h3>
        <p class="text-emerald-100/90 text-base font-body leading-relaxed">
          Cada línea de código es una decisión arquitectónica. Me aseguro de que los cimientos sean lo suficientemente sólidos para soportar el crecimiento futuro.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Qué construyo -->
  <div class="mt-40 mb-20 animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.4s;">
    <div
      class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row justify-between lg:items-end mb-20 gap-10"
    >
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <span
          class="font-label text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-emerald-400/90 mb-2 block"
          >Área de Trabajo</span
        >
        <h2
          class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-headline text-emerald-50 leading-tight"
        >
          Qué tipo de <br />Sistemas Construyo.
        </h2>
      </div>
      <div class="max-w-md">
        <p
          class="text-emerald-100/80 font-body text-base italic border-l border-emerald-500/20 pl-6 py-2 leading-relaxed"
        >
          "El código que no podés leer en seis meses no es tuyo — es deuda técnica disfrazada de solución."
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 md:gap-10">
      <!-- Interfaces de Alto Rendimiento -->
      <div
        class="md:col-span-2 bg-emerald-950/20 blob-card p-10 md:p-14 flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[380px] relative overflow-hidden group border border-emerald-500/10 hover:border-emerald-500/20 transition-all duration-700"
      >
        <div
          class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-80 h-80 bg-emerald-500/5 rounded-full blur-[100px] -mr-40 -mt-40 group-hover:bg-emerald-500/10 transition-all"
        >
        </div>
        <div class="relative z-10">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-10">
            <div
              class="w-12 h-12 bg-emerald-500/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-400 border border-emerald-500/10"
            >
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-headline text-3xl text-emerald-50">
              Interfaces de Alto Rendimiento
            </h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-emerald-100/80 text-base font-body leading-relaxed max-w-lg">
            Construyo frontends que cargan rápido y se mantienen rápidos: arquitectura orientada a componentes, cero JavaScript innecesario en el cliente, y métricas de Core Web Vitals como requisito no negociable desde el diseño.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="relative z-10 pt-10 flex items-center gap-4">
          <div class="h-[1px] w-16 bg-emerald-500/30"></div>
          <span class="font-label text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-emerald-300/70">
            Astro · React · TypeScript · Tailwind
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Arquitectura que Escala -->
      <div
        class="bg-emerald-950/20 blob-card p-10 md:p-14 relative overflow-hidden group border border-emerald-500/10 hover:border-emerald-500/20 transition-all duration-700 flex flex-col justify-between"
      >
        <div
          class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-64 h-64 bg-emerald-400/5 rounded-full blur-[80px] -ml-32 -mb-32 group-hover:bg-emerald-400/10 transition-all"
        >
        </div>
        <div class="relative z-10">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-10">
            <div
              class="w-12 h-12 bg-emerald-900/40 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-400 border border-emerald-500/10 shadow-inner"
            >
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="3" width="7" height="7"></rect><rect x="14" y="3" width="7" height="7"></rect><rect x="14" y="14" width="7" height="7"></rect><rect x="3" y="14" width="7" height="7"></rect></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-headline text-2xl text-emerald-50">
              Arquitectura que Escala
            </h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-emerald-100/80 text-sm font-body leading-relaxed">
            Diseño sistemas con separación de responsabilidades real. Capas bien definidas, dependencias hacia adentro, y lógica de negocio aislada de frameworks para que el código sobreviva al tiempo.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="relative z-10 pt-8">
          <span class="font-label text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-emerald-300/70">
            Clean · Hexagonal · DDD
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Sistemas Full Stack -->
      <div
        class="md:col-span-3 bg-emerald-950/20 blob-card p-10 md:p-14 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-10 items-start md:items-center border border-emerald-500/10 hover:border-emerald-500/20 transition-all duration-700 relative overflow-hidden group"
      >
        <div
          class="absolute right-0 top-0 w-96 h-96 bg-emerald-500/3 rounded-full blur-[120px] -mr-48 -mt-48 group-hover:bg-emerald-500/8 transition-all"
        >
        </div>
        <div
          class="w-full md:w-16 h-16 bg-emerald-500/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-400 border border-emerald-500/10 shrink-0"
        >
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><ellipse cx="12" cy="5" rx="9" ry="3"></ellipse><path d="M3 5V19A9 3 0 0 0 21 19V5"></path><path d="M3 12A9 3 0 0 0 21 12"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="relative z-10 space-y-4 flex-1">
          <h3 class="font-headline text-2xl text-emerald-50">Sistemas Full Stack con Criterio</h3>
          <p class="text-emerald-100/80 text-base font-body leading-relaxed max-w-3xl">
            No solo hago que funcione. Diseño el sistema completo — API, base de datos, despliegue — con las mismas exigencias que el frontend: tipado estricto, contratos explícitos entre capas, y observabilidad desde el día uno. El objetivo no es terminar la feature; es que otro desarrollador pueda tocar ese código seis meses después sin miedo.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="relative z-10 shrink-0">
          <span class="font-label text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-emerald-300/70 whitespace-nowrap">
            Node · PostgreSQL · Docker · CI/CD
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
